tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE medical_image_analysis (
    image_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    patient_id UUID,
    image_data BYTES,
    diagnosis TEXT,
    algorithm_used TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE ImagesDiagnoses (
    image_id UUID,
    diagnosis_id UUID,
    algorithm_id UUID,
    diagnosis_date TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (image_id, diagnosis_id, algorithm_id)
);
